import {getColor} from '../utils'
export default {
  props: {
    focus: {
      type: Boolean,
      default: false
    },
    error: {
      type: Boolean
    },
    errorColor: {
      type: String
    },
    disabled: {
      type: Boolean
    }
  },
  computed: {
    lineClass () {
      return {
        focus: this.focus,
        error: this.error
      }
    },
    errorStyle () {
      return {
        'background-color': this.error ? getColor(this.errorColor) : ''
      }
    }
  }
}
